Pod-Help version 1.00
=====================

Pod::Help is a simple wrapper module to automatically display the
POD of a script or program when it is called with a specific
parameter.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More
  Pod::Perldoc

